Class ProRataRedistributionStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.payment.DistributionStrategy
      • gw.api.web.payment.ProRataDistributionStrategy
        • gw.api.web.payment.ProRataRedistributionStrategy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProRataReversedPaymentAmountRedistributionStrategy

    public class ProRataRedistributionStrategy
extends ProRataDistributionStrategy
    Class to determine the priority algorithm to redistribute excess funds towards a list of dist items. The items presumably already have amounts distributed on them, and these amounts will remain, we will only distribute the excess funds on top of these distributions.
